examples.en: It remains one of nature's secrets.
Hunger is nature's way of telling you to eat.
Disease is nature's way of keeping the population down.
Volcanoes display some of nature's most powerful forces at work.
The endorphins released during exercise are nature's pain relief.
I think I feel nature's call coming on. *
At first glance he was one of nature's second fiddles. A walking bloody hard luck story. *
